rgens, and location details with bold CTAs for online orders.","premium":false,"price":null,"purchase_url":null,"long_description":"**Fast-Food Restaurant Landing Page Template**\n\nA bold, dark-themed landing page template tailored for fast-food and casual restaurants that want to highlight their signature menu, allergens, and location.\n\n## Key Features\n- **Hero section** with strong branding, hours, and dual CTAs for ordering and viewing the menu.\n- **Best-sellers grid** to spotlight star products with pricing and add-to-cart buttons.\n- **Structured menu layout** with burger, sandwich, and bucket categories plus downloadable PDF menu.\n- **Allergen information table** for clear, compliant communication of major allergens.\n- **Location & contact block** with address, hours, phone, and embedded map.\n\n## Primary Use Case\nIdeal for local fast-food, burger joints, and takeaway restaurants needing a ready-made, conversion-focused landing page to drive online and in-store orders while clearly presenting their offer and allergen information.","custom_domain":null,"favicon_light_url":null,"favicon_dark_url":null,"dns_verified":null,"dns_verified_at":null,"dns_a_record":null,"netlify_apex_exists":null,"netlify_www_exists":null,"netlify_verified_at":null,"custom_domain_added_at":null,"netlify_site_id":null,"umami_website_id":null,"umami_share_id":null,"analytics_enabled":false,"gtm_container_id":null,"remix_source":{},"credit_remix_source":false}]